data.purpose: To consider and approve Unaudited Financial Results (Standalone and Consolidated) of the Company for the quarter and half year ended September 30, 2024

SATIN CREDITCARE NETWORK LIMITED has informed the Exchange about Board Meeting to be held on 08-Nov-2024 to inter-alia consider and approve the Unaudited Financial results of the Company for the Half Yearly ended September 2024 .
To consider fund raising proposal by way of issuance of listed, secured, non-convertible bonds on private placement basis.
